# MediAssist Pro — Environment Variables
#
# This app does not use a build process or .env files.
# Credentials are set directly in js/supabase.js.
#
# Copy the two values below from:
# Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API
#
# SUPABASE_URL      = https://YOUR_PROJECT_ID.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY = eyJhbGci...  (anon/public key — safe to expose in frontend)
#
# ⚠️  Never commit your service_role key to this repo.
